post {
  url: http://localhost:5000/api/v1/artisan/:artisan_oid/product/
  body: json
  auth: inherit
}

params:path {
  artisan_oid: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
}

docs {
  **JSON payload structure** (Fields with `null` are *optional*, all others are **required**)**:**
  
  ```json
  {
      "name": "required",
      "summary": "required",
      "description": "required",
      "price": "1.00",
      "shipping_weight": "1.00",
      "height": null,
      "length": null,
      "width": null,
      "size": null
  }
  ```
  
  The example JSON payload used in Chapter 17 was:
  
  ```json
  {
    "name": "Fireproof Dragon-Cradle Blanket",
